com.googlecode.cqengine.persistence.support

Class FilteredObjectStore<O>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.googlecode.cqengine.persistence.support.FilteredObjectStore<O>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ObjectStore<O>

    public class FilteredObjectStore<O>
extends Object
implements ObjectStore<O>
    Wraps an ObjectStore and filters objects returned by its iterator to ensure they match a given query.

    Note this wrapper does not support any method except iterator(QueryOptions)! All other methods will throw UnsupportedOperationException.

    Author:
    niall.gallagher
